1
00:00:00,540 --> 00:00:02,870
(Episode 125)

2
00:00:02,910 --> 00:00:04,180
Eun Hye.

3
00:00:04,810 --> 00:00:08,680
So, you're my Eun Hye.

4
00:00:09,780 --> 00:00:12,450
Don't forgive me.

5
00:00:13,180 --> 00:00:17,160
I cast you out and mistreated you.

6
00:00:18,060 --> 00:00:20,230
I ignored you.

7
00:00:20,990 --> 00:00:22,060
Father.

8
00:00:22,360 --> 00:00:25,900
What am I supposed to do
with the rest of my life?

9
00:00:26,730 --> 00:00:29,930
How can I atone for my sins?

10
00:00:30,470 --> 00:00:32,840
Not even recognizing my own daughter.

11
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:34,870
Oh, dear...

12
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:40,410
The fact that I can see you again...

13
00:00:41,750 --> 00:00:44,420
feels like a dream, Father.

14
00:00:45,950 --> 00:00:47,850
Eun Hye.

15
00:00:52,120 --> 00:00:55,390
Eun Hye, how did you endure...

16
00:00:55,730 --> 00:00:58,730
all those cruel years?

17
00:00:59,630 --> 00:01:02,870
If only I had given my blessing...

18
00:01:02,870 --> 00:01:04,840
when Dong Seok wanted to marry you,

19
00:01:05,440 --> 00:01:09,110
you wouldn't have suffered so much.

20
00:01:09,110 --> 00:01:11,280
- Father.
- My goodness.

21
00:01:14,010 --> 00:01:16,010
It's my fault.

22
00:01:16,580 --> 00:01:18,750
I'm the one to blame.

23
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:21,950
Don't say that, Father.

24
00:01:23,620 --> 00:01:27,030
I couldn't accept that
my own granddaughter's mother...

25
00:01:27,460 --> 00:01:28,960
had an intellectual disability.

26
00:01:29,030 --> 00:01:31,900
I'm just a cruel old man.

27
00:01:32,930 --> 00:01:36,370
After all this time,
how could I have the nerve to...

28
00:01:37,540 --> 00:01:43,310
I have no right to call you my daughter.

29
00:01:43,740 --> 00:01:47,410
Don't forgive me.
I'm the one who deserves to die.

30
00:01:47,780 --> 00:01:49,850
I deserve to die.

31
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,950
No, Father.

32
00:01:54,050 --> 00:01:58,060
I'm just so grateful...

33
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:01,190
that you're alive and well.

34
00:02:01,990 --> 00:02:07,130
I never dreamed I'd be able to see you.

35
00:02:07,930 --> 00:02:10,970
I'm so happy,
and it feels like a dream, Father.

36
00:02:12,870 --> 00:02:13,910
Father.

37
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:17,180
Thank you for not forgetting me...

38
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:20,950
and for finding me, Father.

39
00:02:23,380 --> 00:02:24,780
Father.

40
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:26,350
I'm sorry.

41
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:28,350
I'm so sorry.

42
00:02:29,590 --> 00:02:35,260
From now on, I'll make it all up to you.

43
00:02:36,490 --> 00:02:39,900
I'll wipe away all your tears...

44
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:45,770
from your past years of suffering.

45
00:02:50,170 --> 00:02:53,310
Jang Mi, come here.

46
00:02:55,650 --> 00:02:56,780
Grandfather.

47
00:02:59,420 --> 00:03:01,350
Yes...

48
00:03:02,150 --> 00:03:05,060
You are my flesh and blood.

49
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:07,990
My real granddaughter.

50
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:17,740
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

51
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:20,310
I wonder how our Jun Ho is doing.

52
00:03:21,010 --> 00:03:24,140
Now that he knows
Kang Baek Ho is Choi Ha Joon,

53
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:26,010
the majority shareholder of Dream Group,

54
00:03:26,580 --> 00:03:28,310
he must be worried.

55
00:03:32,250 --> 00:03:35,050
Jun Ho, I found out who Choi Ha Joon is.

56
00:03:35,850 --> 00:03:37,790
You did? Who is it?

57
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,960
If you found him,
we need to meet him right away...

58
00:03:40,290 --> 00:03:42,360
and do whatever it takes
to win him over to our side.

59
00:03:42,460 --> 00:03:45,130
It's Kang Baek Ho. He's Choi Ha Joon.

60
00:03:45,730 --> 00:03:46,730
What did you say?

61
00:03:48,100 --> 00:03:49,870
Kang Baek Ho is Choi Ha Joon?

62
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:54,670
How can he possibly be Choi Ha Joon?

63
00:03:56,470 --> 00:03:58,110
Kang Baek Ho is Choi Ha Joon?

64
00:03:59,540 --> 00:04:00,610
How can this be?

65
00:04:02,250 --> 00:04:04,680
Kang Jun Ho. Get a hold of yourself.

66
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,150
If Kang Baek Ho is Choi Ha Joon,

67
00:04:07,350 --> 00:04:09,920
all of our dreams could go up in smoke.

68
00:04:10,660 --> 00:04:12,760
I can't believe
something like this has happened.

69
00:04:12,820 --> 00:04:14,030
Is that true?

70
00:04:14,690 --> 00:04:16,460
I just can't believe it.

71
00:04:16,460 --> 00:04:18,430
Jin Hong Ju knew...

72
00:04:18,930 --> 00:04:20,870
that Kang Baek Ho was
the majority shareholder.

73
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,100
She knew?

74
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:26,700
This can't be.

75
00:04:27,970 --> 00:04:32,810
If Kang Baek Ho is Choi Ha Joon,
there's no way he'll ever be on our side.

76
00:04:34,250 --> 00:04:36,650
Now he'll use his position
as the majority shareholder...

77
00:04:36,650 --> 00:04:38,320
to oust us for sure.

78
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:39,520
No.

79
00:04:40,490 --> 00:04:41,750
Kang Baek Ho himself...

80
00:04:42,650 --> 00:04:45,560
doesn't seem to know
that he's Choi Ha Joon yet.

81
00:04:45,790 --> 00:04:47,090
He'll find out soon enough.

82
00:04:48,890 --> 00:04:50,760
I'm going crazy just thinking about it.

83
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:55,530
I might have to spend the rest of my life
groveling under that bastard.

84
00:04:58,370 --> 00:05:00,200
Yes, that's it exactly.

85
00:05:00,470 --> 00:05:02,910
- Pardon?
- What if that old man, Chairman Ma,

86
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:06,180
doesn't know that
Kang Baek Ho is Choi Ha Joon?

87
00:05:06,710 --> 00:05:07,710
I'm not sure.

88
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:12,650
That's probably it.
He's been quiet because he doesn't know.

89
00:05:12,780 --> 00:05:15,390
Yes, Chairman Ma definitely doesn't know.

90
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:18,990
Think about it.
Kang Baek Ho is the majority shareholder.

91
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:21,660
Why was he abandoned
and put up for adoption?

92
00:05:22,130 --> 00:05:25,430
There must be some mystery
hidden in the past.

93
00:05:25,530 --> 00:05:28,930
It could very well be
Chairman Ma's Achilles' heel.

94
00:05:29,100 --> 00:05:30,670
You could be right.

95
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:34,110
After all, Chairman Ma
has been exercising his rights...

96
00:05:34,110 --> 00:05:35,610
on behalf of the majority shareholder,
Choi Ha Joon.

97
00:05:36,710 --> 00:05:39,010
We have to find
Chairman Ma's Achilles' heel.

98
00:05:39,510 --> 00:05:41,480
We need to find it to survive.

99
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,980
I'll start by digging into that.

100
00:05:48,990 --> 00:05:51,220
Of course I did.

101
00:05:51,420 --> 00:05:53,730
He and I were the best of friends.

102
00:05:53,930 --> 00:05:58,800
I'm the one who gave you this golden toad
and golden spoon as a first-birthday gift.

103
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,470
Then perhaps the Chairman...

104
00:06:02,870 --> 00:06:05,800
knows why there was a fire
at my grandfather's house.

105
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:09,040
Since they were close friends,
he must know the details.

106
00:06:10,340 --> 00:06:12,480
I'm so eager to hear
what he says about my grandfather.

107
00:06:13,410 --> 00:06:16,550
I wonder if the Chairman and my mother
have met by now.

108
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:20,120
To think you were so close,

109
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:22,420
but I didn't even recognize you.

110
00:06:23,350 --> 00:06:25,460
I thought you were dead,

111
00:06:26,290 --> 00:06:29,030
so I never even thought to look for you.

112
00:06:29,290 --> 00:06:31,060
When I was little,

113
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:34,300
I used to wonder
why my parents abandoned me,

114
00:06:34,830 --> 00:06:36,400
and I resented them for it.

115
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:40,640
But after the ordeal of taking an exam
for someone else...

116
00:06:41,410 --> 00:06:43,110
and even contemplating suicide,

117
00:06:43,810 --> 00:06:46,380
I suppose I matured.

118
00:06:47,550 --> 00:06:50,110
My parents...

119
00:06:50,650 --> 00:06:52,650
must have had their reasons.

120
00:06:54,020 --> 00:06:55,320
My resentment faded,

121
00:06:55,950 --> 00:06:58,120
and my longing for them only grew.

122
00:06:59,790 --> 00:07:00,830
Yes.

123
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:04,860
- I see.
- But...

124
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:08,030
is my real name Eun Hye?

125
00:07:08,030 --> 00:07:10,130
Yes, it is.

126
00:07:10,870 --> 00:07:13,740
Here. Take a look at this.

127
00:07:14,270 --> 00:07:17,180
This baby is you, Eun Hye.

128
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:20,950
And this is your mother.

129
00:07:20,950 --> 00:07:22,080
Her name is Seong Sil.

130
00:07:22,780 --> 00:07:25,650
This is the first time you've seen
a picture of your mother, isn't it?

131
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:34,060
So this is what my mom looked like.

132
00:07:38,460 --> 00:07:41,030
Mom...

133
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:44,640
I really...

134
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:48,710
had a mother.

135
00:07:54,250 --> 00:07:55,580
I'm sorry.

136
00:07:57,580 --> 00:08:00,520
I'm so sorry, Eun Hye.

137
00:08:01,090 --> 00:08:04,690
Mom.

138
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:05,920
Mom.

139
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:09,460
Mom.

140
00:08:11,860 --> 00:08:12,860
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

141
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:14,100
What? Bait?

142
00:08:14,570 --> 00:08:18,040
Yes. Chairman Ma and Secretary Kim
acting separately...

143
00:08:18,940 --> 00:08:21,040
- feels suspicious.
- What do you mean?

144
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:23,040
What's so suspicious about it?

145
00:08:23,210 --> 00:08:26,980
While Chairman Ma was at the hospital
for a surprise checkup,

146
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:30,310
Secretary Kim grabbed an envelope
and rushed off somewhere,

147
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:33,120
- so I followed him.
- And?

148
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:36,090
But it turned out to be
a pointless errand.

149
00:08:36,550 --> 00:08:39,960
Besides, it isn't even time
for Chairman Ma's regular checkup.

150
00:08:40,730 --> 00:08:41,730
That's right.

151
00:08:41,730 --> 00:08:43,530
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

152
00:08:43,530 --> 00:08:45,030
That crafty old fox...

153
00:08:45,430 --> 00:08:47,900
must have used Secretary Kim
as a diversion...

154
00:08:48,230 --> 00:08:52,000
while he went to the hospital
to take care of something else.

155
00:08:52,970 --> 00:08:54,510
What could he possibly have been doing?

156
00:08:55,570 --> 00:08:58,140
What was so important
for him to trick you?

157
00:08:58,280 --> 00:08:59,310
I suspect...

158
00:09:00,140 --> 00:09:03,650
he had a DNA test done
for Jung Suk Hee and himself.

159
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:06,480
- Chairman Ma himself, I mean.
- What?

160
00:09:06,750 --> 00:09:07,920
Chairman Ma did it himself?

161
00:09:08,090 --> 00:09:10,520
Since he didn't trust the DNA test
Secretary Kim did,

162
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:13,960
he must have wanted to confirm it
with his own two hands.

163
00:09:14,130 --> 00:09:15,260
No, that can't happen.

164
00:09:15,660 --> 00:09:17,360
Something like that can't happen.
Absolutely not.

165
00:09:18,330 --> 00:09:21,430
I can't let Chairman Ma find out
Jung Suk Hee is his daughter.

166
00:09:21,430 --> 00:09:22,530
No way!

167
00:09:23,730 --> 00:09:26,740
Chae Hwa Young, that vicious woman,

168
00:09:27,670 --> 00:09:29,440
stole your necklace...

169
00:09:30,140 --> 00:09:32,340
and even forged the DNA test results...

170
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:35,610
to pretend she was my daughter.

171
00:09:35,610 --> 00:09:37,050
That's just unbelievable.

172
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:42,290
So that's why Chae Hwa Young
was reinstated as CEO.

173
00:09:42,420 --> 00:09:45,720
Do you really think I would fall...

174
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:48,030
for Chae Hwa Young's obvious lies?

175
00:09:48,630 --> 00:09:51,100
Reinstating her as CEO...

176
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:55,070
was a plan to expose
whatever else she was up to.

177
00:09:55,700 --> 00:09:59,470
Actually, we hid the fact
that my mom recovered her memories,

178
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,870
and we took Chae Hwa Young's slush fund.

179
00:10:02,010 --> 00:10:03,470
Yes, I knew.

180
00:10:03,740 --> 00:10:04,740
You did?

181
00:10:05,410 --> 00:10:06,410
How?

182
00:10:06,540 --> 00:10:07,680
You little rascal.

183
00:10:08,180 --> 00:10:11,550
Come on, don't underestimate
your grandfather's information network.

184
00:10:12,020 --> 00:10:13,150
Thanks to that,

185
00:10:13,420 --> 00:10:17,290
I was able to find Suk Hee easily.

186
00:10:18,860 --> 00:10:19,990
So that's how.

187
00:10:21,290 --> 00:10:22,690
By the way,

188
00:10:22,830 --> 00:10:26,360
when did your memories from the past...

189
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:28,100
start coming back?

190
00:10:28,530 --> 00:10:31,900
My memories were coming back
in bits and pieces for a while,

191
00:10:32,740 --> 00:10:35,070
but the shock of Seo Rin's death...

192
00:10:35,470 --> 00:10:37,510
seems to have brought them all back
completely.

193
00:10:39,380 --> 00:10:40,810
How could Chae Hwa Young
do that to the child...

194
00:10:40,880 --> 00:10:42,850
she raised as her own daughter
for 30 years?

195
00:10:43,550 --> 00:10:46,720
I can never forgive Chae Hwa Young.

196
00:10:47,180 --> 00:10:48,190
Right.

197
00:10:49,050 --> 00:10:51,190
We can't just let her be.

198
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:52,960
Of course not.

199
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:56,030
Now...

200
00:10:56,660 --> 00:10:59,900
all the pieces of the puzzle
seem to be falling into place.

201
00:11:00,700 --> 00:11:03,900
The reason that wench Chae Hwa Young
got rid of our Seo Rin...

202
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:07,540
is probably because Seo Rin...

203
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:12,210
found out that you are my daughter.

204
00:11:12,380 --> 00:11:15,280
Chae Hwa Young was also responsible
for the death of Bok Gil, my father.

205
00:11:16,150 --> 00:11:19,920
She staged a hit-and-run to hide the fact
that Seo Rin and I are twins.

206
00:11:20,250 --> 00:11:25,420
Jang Mi and I
can never forgive Chae Hwa Young.

207
00:11:25,420 --> 00:11:26,520
Grandfather,

208
00:11:27,020 --> 00:11:29,830
you need to make a firm decision now.

209
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:32,330
I know you've covered
for Chae Hwa Young's corruption...

210
00:11:32,330 --> 00:11:33,730
to protect Dream Group...

211
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:37,740
and to prevent the stock price
from falling this whole time.

212
00:11:38,270 --> 00:11:39,570
But take a good look.

213
00:11:40,100 --> 00:11:42,740
If you had put Chae Hwa Young away sooner,

214
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:44,510
Seo Rin...

215
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:48,380
We might have been able
to save our innocent Seo Rin.

216
00:11:50,950 --> 00:11:51,980
I'm sorry.

217
00:11:53,750 --> 00:11:54,790
I was blinded...

218
00:11:56,150 --> 00:12:00,420
by my petty calculations
to protect the company,

219
00:12:01,590 --> 00:12:05,260
and let my daughter and granddaughter
suffer so terribly.

220
00:12:05,930 --> 00:12:07,500
I just looked the other way.

221
00:12:09,530 --> 00:12:11,270
Chae Hwa Young, that wench.

222
00:12:12,470 --> 00:12:13,800
That vicious wench.

223
00:12:15,010 --> 00:12:18,010
I can't just hand her over
to the police...

224
00:12:19,310 --> 00:12:23,280
and let her eat
three square meals a day in prison.

225
00:12:24,680 --> 00:12:28,490
How do you plan on punishing her?

226
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:41,800
I should have known when he called
for the fake Park Young Mi again.

227
00:12:42,330 --> 00:12:44,700
That big-mouthed wench...

228
00:12:45,040 --> 00:12:46,840
must have spilled everything
about my plan.

229
00:12:47,040 --> 00:12:50,210
If Chairman Ma personally
confirmed the DNA test results,

230
00:12:50,710 --> 00:12:52,040
then the situation is serious.

231
00:12:53,040 --> 00:12:55,950
- What should we do?
- I can't just run away now.

232
00:12:56,780 --> 00:12:59,750
First, I need to confront him
and find out.

233
00:12:59,920 --> 00:13:02,890
What? You're going to face
Chairman Ma directly?

234
00:13:02,990 --> 00:13:07,120
That old man, Chairman Ma,
hasn't shown me his cards yet.

235
00:13:07,860 --> 00:13:10,130
Exactly how much he knows,

236
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:13,230
and what schemes
that half-wit Jung Suk Hee...

237
00:13:13,300 --> 00:13:14,600
is pulling in my house.

238
00:13:15,130 --> 00:13:17,030
I need to see it with my own two eyes...

239
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:19,540
and finish them off.

240
00:13:21,170 --> 00:13:22,170
Understood.

241
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:24,140
I'll take you home right away.

242
00:13:39,990 --> 00:13:40,990
What are you doing here?

243
00:13:41,560 --> 00:13:44,930
Why are you making ramyeon in my house?
Who said you could?

244
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:48,300
Hey, you're not supposed to bother
even a dog when it's eating.

245
00:13:48,570 --> 00:13:49,770
Let's talk after I'm done eating.

246
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:52,800
Unbelievable.

247
00:13:58,280 --> 00:13:59,280
What's this?

248
00:13:59,380 --> 00:14:03,750
I bought it to eat with Jun Ho,
but he wasn't there, so I brought it back.

249
00:14:08,920 --> 00:14:10,250
What do you think you're doing?

250
00:14:11,990 --> 00:14:13,320
I didn't buy that for you.

251
00:14:14,430 --> 00:14:16,960
Don't be so cheap.

252
00:14:17,290 --> 00:14:18,660
Give me a break.

253
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,930
Can you sew this button on for me?

254
00:14:24,540 --> 00:14:27,710
This is so absurd that I'm speechless.

255
00:14:27,710 --> 00:14:30,340
Did you think I'd just say,
"Oh, of course, dear,"

256
00:14:30,340 --> 00:14:31,740
and do it for you?

257
00:14:31,840 --> 00:14:35,810
I don't have anything else to wear.
You always did it for me.

258
00:14:35,910 --> 00:14:37,250
You've got to be kidding me.

259
00:14:37,620 --> 00:14:38,880
My goodness.

260
00:14:41,020 --> 00:14:43,290
Go ask that witch Chae Hwa Young to do it!

261
00:14:43,290 --> 00:14:44,690
Or take it to the cleaners.

262
00:14:45,060 --> 00:14:47,360
Fine, then finalize the divorce.

263
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:50,660
Since we haven't signed the papers,
you're still my wife.

264
00:14:50,660 --> 00:14:53,130
Aren't wives supposed to take care
of their husbands?

265
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:54,330
Listen to you.

266
00:14:54,830 --> 00:14:56,130
You shameless punk!

267
00:15:00,300 --> 00:15:01,340
Come on.

268
00:15:08,250 --> 00:15:09,480
(Minutes
of the General Shareholders' Meeting)

269
00:15:09,550 --> 00:15:11,650
(Shareholders: Choi Ha Joon, by proxy,
Ma Dae Chang, in person)

270
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:14,750
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

271
00:15:16,790 --> 00:15:17,890
Something's not right.

272
00:15:18,820 --> 00:15:21,560
It seems like Kang Baek Ho
only just found out he's Choi Ha Joon.

273
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:24,700
But Chairman Ma cast
Choi Ha Joon's proxy vote...

274
00:15:24,700 --> 00:15:25,900
at the shareholders' meeting.

275
00:15:34,170 --> 00:15:35,840
Why is the house so quiet? Is no one home?

276
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:38,640
The Chairman came back
from his medical check-up...

277
00:15:38,710 --> 00:15:39,880
and then went out again.

278
00:15:40,180 --> 00:15:43,380
Really? Has anyone else stopped by?

279
00:15:43,380 --> 00:15:44,650
Anyone else? Like who?

280
00:15:44,950 --> 00:15:47,320
No one's been here besides family.

281
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:48,850
So Oh Jang Mi hasn't been here either?

282
00:15:49,050 --> 00:15:52,090
- But Oh Jang Mi is family.
- What about Yeom San Wol?

283
00:15:52,120 --> 00:15:53,860
She went out earlier and hasn't returned.

284
00:15:56,490 --> 00:15:57,560
Hey, Yeom San Wol.

285
00:15:57,730 --> 00:16:01,530
What have you been doing,
running around instead of staying home?

286
00:16:02,570 --> 00:16:04,970
What's wrong with you?

287
00:16:05,100 --> 00:16:08,140
I can go wherever I want.
Why is it any of your business?

288
00:16:08,340 --> 00:16:09,740
Am I the family watchdog?

289
00:16:09,810 --> 00:16:12,080
You've got an answer for everything,
don't you?

290
00:16:12,680 --> 00:16:14,040
Where did the Chairman go?

291
00:16:14,040 --> 00:16:16,680
Isn't it your job to assist the Chairman?

292
00:16:17,150 --> 00:16:19,350
How dare you raise your voice at me
when you're neglecting your duties?

293
00:16:19,480 --> 00:16:21,050
The Chairman's not here?

294
00:16:21,550 --> 00:16:23,050
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

295
00:16:23,150 --> 00:16:25,520
- Welcome, Chairman.
- Hello.

296
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:29,060
So this is where you live.

297
00:16:29,260 --> 00:16:33,060
Yes. I've been living here happily
in my own way.

298
00:16:33,530 --> 00:16:34,670
Please sit, Father.

299
00:16:34,970 --> 00:16:36,070
All right.

300
00:16:37,170 --> 00:16:38,840
Goodness.

301
00:16:39,770 --> 00:16:41,140
You're living in such a cramped place.

302
00:16:43,470 --> 00:16:45,280
This is all my fault.

303
00:16:45,980 --> 00:16:47,140
I'm so sorry.

304
00:16:47,540 --> 00:16:48,750
You're so frail,

305
00:16:48,750 --> 00:16:50,810
yet you've suffered so much
running this business.

306
00:16:50,810 --> 00:16:52,120
I wasn't suffering.

307
00:16:52,550 --> 00:16:55,920
Bok Gil's children,
Tae Pyung and Tae Sook,

308
00:16:56,420 --> 00:16:59,460
treated me so well,
like I was their mother.

309
00:16:59,660 --> 00:17:02,330
And of course,
they took good care of my Jang Mi too.

310
00:17:02,430 --> 00:17:03,660
That's right, Grandfather.

311
00:17:04,230 --> 00:17:05,600
My father, Oh Bok Gil,

312
00:17:06,300 --> 00:17:09,800
truly loved and protected
my mother and me.

313
00:17:09,970 --> 00:17:13,100
Yes. He was a very good man.

314
00:17:14,070 --> 00:17:15,810
That wretched woman, Chae Hwa Young...

315
00:17:17,610 --> 00:17:18,610
- Here.
- Thanks.

316
00:17:18,610 --> 00:17:22,150
Your name is Oh Tae Pyung, right?

317
00:17:23,010 --> 00:17:27,120
If there's anything you need or want,
just tell me. I'll take care of it.

318
00:17:28,050 --> 00:17:31,560
We should start by moving you
to a bigger house.

319
00:17:31,620 --> 00:17:32,790
What do you say?

320
00:17:33,120 --> 00:17:35,130
No, that's all right, Chairman.

321
00:17:36,360 --> 00:17:37,760
For us, all we want...

322
00:17:38,860 --> 00:17:41,730
is to get revenge on Chae Hwa Young
for our father's death.

323
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:43,400
That's all we want.

324
00:17:43,470 --> 00:17:46,640
That's right. We're almost done
gathering the evidence, Grandfather.

325
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:50,510
- We just need to find the murder weapon.
- Right.

326
00:17:50,610 --> 00:17:54,110
That devil of a woman, Chae Hwa Young.

327
00:17:54,780 --> 00:17:56,050
It's my life's greatest regret...

328
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:59,950
that I didn't deal with her sooner
because I was worried about the company.

329
00:18:00,420 --> 00:18:03,550
To think she ruined
Eun Hye's life like this.

330
00:18:03,850 --> 00:18:08,390
Is Chae Hwa Young still going around
pretending to be your daughter?

331
00:18:08,760 --> 00:18:09,790
Yes.

332
00:18:11,230 --> 00:18:13,360
She said that if it became known
she was my daughter,

333
00:18:13,360 --> 00:18:16,130
it could cause a lot of complications,

334
00:18:16,330 --> 00:18:18,340
so she suggested we keep it between us.

335
00:18:20,040 --> 00:18:21,610
And I played along.

336
00:18:22,170 --> 00:18:25,210
But now that I've found you,

337
00:18:26,340 --> 00:18:29,510
I'll summon her at once.
I won't let her get away with this.

338
00:18:29,780 --> 00:18:30,880
But sir,

339
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:34,690
if she finds out
that you've found your real daughter,

340
00:18:34,990 --> 00:18:38,590
Chae Hwa Young won't leave her alone.
She's a murderer, after all.

341
00:18:38,760 --> 00:18:42,390
That's right.
She even killed her own daughter, Seo Rin.

342
00:18:42,760 --> 00:18:44,900
You're right.

343
00:18:45,930 --> 00:18:47,300
If I make the wrong move,

344
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:51,740
I could put my precious daughter
and granddaughter in danger again.

345
00:18:52,370 --> 00:18:53,400
However,

346
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:56,410
I'm not just going to stand by.

347
00:19:10,190 --> 00:19:11,220
Dad.

348
00:19:11,820 --> 00:19:12,990
Where have you been?

349
00:19:17,260 --> 00:19:20,100
I had to make some revisions to my will,

350
00:19:20,900 --> 00:19:24,300
so I was just at the lawyer's office.

351
00:19:25,900 --> 00:19:28,410
What? Your will?

352
00:19:28,710 --> 00:19:29,710
Yes.

353
00:19:31,810 --> 00:19:34,240
You're my daughter,

354
00:19:35,180 --> 00:19:37,750
so shouldn't I be leaving everything
to you?

355
00:19:38,420 --> 00:19:40,320
- What?
- Why so surprised?

356
00:19:40,820 --> 00:19:42,020
Do you think I'm lying?

357
00:19:42,650 --> 00:19:43,650
No.

358
00:19:44,350 --> 00:19:45,560
It feels like a dream.

359
00:19:46,260 --> 00:19:50,190
Dad, are you really going to give me...

360
00:19:51,130 --> 00:19:52,300
Dream Group...

361
00:19:53,100 --> 00:19:55,270
and everything?

362
00:19:55,270 --> 00:19:56,700
Yes.

363
00:19:57,370 --> 00:19:59,440
You're my precious daughter.

364
00:20:01,840 --> 00:20:05,240
I'm not going to live forever.

365
00:20:05,310 --> 00:20:06,910
Why would I hold onto everything?

366
00:20:07,610 --> 00:20:10,250
Of course, it should go to you,
my own flesh and blood.

367
00:20:12,880 --> 00:20:14,080
I just can't believe it.

368
00:20:14,790 --> 00:20:16,120
Thank you, Dad.

369
00:20:16,120 --> 00:20:17,750
Thank you so much.

370
00:20:18,820 --> 00:20:22,060
There's no need for tears.
It's only natural.

371
00:20:22,860 --> 00:20:24,530
This has been my dream for so long.

372
00:20:25,560 --> 00:20:28,500
I never thought this day would come.

373
00:20:28,770 --> 00:20:31,300
Please tell me this isn't a dream.

374
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:34,940
It's not. It's real.

375
00:20:35,970 --> 00:20:36,970
Dad...

376
00:20:38,410 --> 00:20:43,710
From now on,
you will be the true master of Dream.

377
00:20:44,450 --> 00:20:46,020
As the head of Dream,

378
00:20:46,350 --> 00:20:49,350
you'll need to know every single detail
of the company.

379
00:20:49,520 --> 00:20:52,890
- Of course. You can count on it.
- Soon,

380
00:20:53,490 --> 00:20:55,790
we will go
to the New York branch together,

381
00:20:55,960 --> 00:20:59,460
and I will introduce you as my successor.

382
00:20:59,860 --> 00:21:03,500
I'm confident I can grow the company...

383
00:21:03,800 --> 00:21:05,970
to be several times bigger
than what you've built.

384
00:21:07,700 --> 00:21:08,810
Thank you, Dad.

385
00:21:10,140 --> 00:21:11,170
Good.

386
00:21:11,170 --> 00:21:13,080
The lawyer is coming here tomorrow,

387
00:21:13,140 --> 00:21:15,650
and I'll sign the inheritance papers.
Just so you know.

388
00:21:16,650 --> 00:21:17,650
Yes.

389
00:21:29,330 --> 00:21:30,330
Kang Hyuk.

390
00:21:31,330 --> 00:21:33,400
I'm finally becoming the head of Dream.

391
00:21:33,800 --> 00:21:36,130
Chairman Ma is handing everything
over to me.

392
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:37,400
What?

393
00:21:37,700 --> 00:21:40,000
So Chairman Ma didn't do the DNA test?

394
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:41,710
That's right, you fool.

395
00:21:42,170 --> 00:21:44,170
We were worried sick for nothing.

396
00:21:45,040 --> 00:21:47,110
Chairman Ma was so busy today...

397
00:21:47,610 --> 00:21:51,180
because he was arranging my inheritance
as his daughter.

398
00:21:51,280 --> 00:21:53,620
He was just sorting out
the procedures and taxes.

399
00:21:54,920 --> 00:21:57,820
- I see.
- He's rewriting his will tomorrow.

400
00:21:58,590 --> 00:21:59,960
Once that's done,

401
00:22:00,460 --> 00:22:03,630
our long-awaited plan
will finally be a huge success.

402
00:22:05,460 --> 00:22:06,930
It really feels like a dream.

403
00:22:07,430 --> 00:22:08,900
This isn't a dream, is it?

404
00:22:09,970 --> 00:22:12,700
- Congratulations in advance, ma'am.
- Thank you.

405
00:22:13,400 --> 00:22:17,110
This was all possible
because you were by my side.

406
00:22:17,910 --> 00:22:20,680
Let's have a celebratory toast
with Jun Ho tomorrow.

407
00:22:21,080 --> 00:22:22,980
It's late.
You should go home and get some rest.

408
00:22:23,180 --> 00:22:24,580
Yes. Good night.

409
00:22:55,910 --> 00:22:58,120
- Hello?
- It's me.

410
00:23:01,550 --> 00:23:04,250
Yes, Dad. What is it?

411
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:07,320
I have something urgent to discuss.

412
00:23:07,960 --> 00:23:09,330
Come to my study now.

413
00:23:09,760 --> 00:23:11,800
I want to get it done
while it's on my mind.

414
00:23:12,060 --> 00:23:13,100
Okay.

415
00:23:13,660 --> 00:23:14,900
Darn it.

416
00:23:14,900 --> 00:23:16,600
That old man never sleeps.

417
00:23:17,370 --> 00:23:19,970
What could be so urgent
that he has to call me at this hour?

418
00:23:20,470 --> 00:23:21,770
It could have waited until tomorrow.

419
00:23:32,050 --> 00:23:33,250
You called for me, Dad?

420
00:23:34,320 --> 00:23:35,390
Yes.

421
00:23:38,290 --> 00:23:39,420
Listen.

422
00:23:40,290 --> 00:23:43,960
I have a feeling
I don't have much longer to live.

423
00:23:45,330 --> 00:23:47,560
Don't say that.
You have to live a long life.

424
00:23:48,270 --> 00:23:50,470
No need to make a fuss.

425
00:23:52,200 --> 00:23:54,670
The reason I called you
in the middle of the night...

426
00:23:56,040 --> 00:23:59,380
is to give you everything I have.

427
00:24:00,240 --> 00:24:01,580
Everything?

428
00:24:01,980 --> 00:24:04,920
The slush fund ledgers
passed down by my predecessors...

429
00:24:04,980 --> 00:24:07,120
and the list
of secret overseas accounts...

430
00:24:07,650 --> 00:24:10,420
are kept in a secret safe in the basement.

431
00:24:10,690 --> 00:24:13,820
You're the only one
who can know about this,

432
00:24:14,190 --> 00:24:16,030
and you must manage it yourself.

433
00:24:16,630 --> 00:24:18,830
- Yes.
- Now.

434
00:24:19,600 --> 00:24:20,700
Let's go down.

435
00:24:23,130 --> 00:24:24,330
What?

436
00:24:24,500 --> 00:24:25,700
I suspected...

437
00:24:25,940 --> 00:24:28,140
that old man had a slush fund,

438
00:24:28,610 --> 00:24:31,010
but who knew the slush fund ledgers
were in the house?

439
00:24:31,880 --> 00:24:34,410
He really is something else.

440
00:24:56,830 --> 00:24:59,770
Oh my goodness, Secretary Kim.
You're still here.

441
00:25:01,910 --> 00:25:03,010
Dad.

442
00:25:03,240 --> 00:25:05,580
Is this the place
you keep the slush fund ledgers?

443
00:25:07,810 --> 00:25:10,710
You vile witch.

444
00:25:15,320 --> 00:25:18,560
Open your eyes and see for yourself.

445
00:25:19,390 --> 00:25:21,990
This proves that I am
Jung Suk Hee's biological father.

446
00:25:22,590 --> 00:25:26,360
- How dare you try to deceive me!
- Dad...

447
00:25:26,830 --> 00:25:28,060
Who are you calling Dad?

448
00:25:28,430 --> 00:25:31,770
You have the nerve to still call me Dad?

449
00:25:32,140 --> 00:25:34,640
No, you're mistaken.

450
00:25:35,270 --> 00:25:39,280
They must have been switched.
Oh Jang Mi swapped my DNA sample...

451
00:25:39,280 --> 00:25:40,410
for Jung Suk Hee's.

452
00:25:40,410 --> 00:25:42,380
Jung Suk Hee had that necklace,
you know...

453
00:25:42,450 --> 00:25:43,510
Enough!

454
00:25:43,780 --> 00:25:47,180
Then, where did Jung Suk Hee
get that necklace?

455
00:25:48,120 --> 00:25:50,190
- Well...
- You little...

456
00:25:51,490 --> 00:25:53,760
You vile creature.

457
00:25:54,190 --> 00:25:57,990
How dare you try to deceive me?

458
00:25:58,260 --> 00:26:03,200
You witch.
You will never see the light of day again.

459
00:26:03,670 --> 00:26:07,840
You're going to spend
the rest of your life here and die!

460
00:26:08,810 --> 00:26:11,810
You'll be reported...

461
00:26:11,810 --> 00:26:15,310
as having gone missing
a month into a business trip abroad.

462
00:26:15,980 --> 00:26:17,910
I'm not going to kill you quickly.

463
00:26:18,520 --> 00:26:20,850
I'm going to make you suffer.

464
00:26:21,120 --> 00:26:25,520
The pain that my Suk Hee, Jang Mi,
and Seo Rin suffered...

465
00:26:25,620 --> 00:26:29,660
I'm going to make you feel
every last bit of it.

466
00:26:29,990 --> 00:26:32,200
And only then will I let you die.

467
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:35,300
- Dad...
- What?

468
00:26:35,630 --> 00:26:39,740
Did you think I've been fooled by you
all this time?

469
00:26:40,040 --> 00:26:45,110
You dared to try
and kill my daughter, Suk Hee,

470
00:26:45,210 --> 00:26:47,340
and kidnap Seo Rin?

471
00:26:48,140 --> 00:26:52,080
As if killing Seo Rin wasn't enough,

472
00:26:52,150 --> 00:26:55,250
you tried to trick me by pretending
to be Ma Eun Hye!

473
00:26:59,520 --> 00:27:02,560
You also killed Bok Gil.
But that's not all, is it?

474
00:27:02,630 --> 00:27:05,600
You killed my daughter, Seo Rin,
with your own two hands.

475
00:27:06,230 --> 00:27:07,830
Did you think I'd let you
get away with it?

476
00:27:09,200 --> 00:27:12,070
Jung Suk Hee, you've come to your senses?

477
00:27:12,800 --> 00:27:14,870
So it was all an act this whole time?

478
00:27:14,940 --> 00:27:17,540
Get ready to pay for all of your crimes.

479
00:27:19,380 --> 00:27:20,480
Ali...

480
00:27:20,540 --> 00:27:22,180
Jung Suk Hee, you're Ali, aren't you?

481
00:27:22,680 --> 00:27:24,710
My money... My 30 million dollars!

482
00:27:58,520 --> 00:28:00,120
(The First Man)

483
00:28:00,280 --> 00:28:02,290
We've brought in Lee Kang Hyuk.

484
00:28:02,550 --> 00:28:04,390
If Chae Hwa Young
and Manager Lee are consumed...

485
00:28:04,390 --> 00:28:07,090
by the fear
that they might betray each other,

486
00:28:07,090 --> 00:28:08,560
they'll have no choice but to confess.

487
00:28:08,860 --> 00:28:11,930
Think carefully, you bastard.

488
00:28:12,100 --> 00:28:17,630
Spit out everything Chae Hwa Young did.

489
00:28:17,730 --> 00:28:21,500
Grandfather probably
made Manager Lee a tempting offer.

490
00:28:21,670 --> 00:28:24,340
- Don't you think he's already talking?
- Manager Lee?

491
00:28:26,510 --> 00:28:28,510
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
